3
00:00:18,640 --> 00:00:20,280
Are you engaged?

4
00:00:20,680 --> 00:00:21,440
Yeah.

5
00:00:22,360 --> 00:00:23,800
We've met each other's parents.

6
00:00:23,800 --> 00:00:25,280
His parents said that

7
00:00:25,280 --> 00:00:26,920
before we went abroad to study,

8
00:00:26,920 --> 00:00:28,960
we'd better get married first

9
00:00:28,960 --> 00:00:30,800
lest he would bully me.

10
00:00:31,560 --> 00:00:32,920
Great.

11
00:00:33,560 --> 00:00:35,080
I envy you so much.

12
00:00:36,440 --> 00:00:38,280
It's supposed to be a blessing.

13
00:00:38,280 --> 00:00:39,920
But why do I feel

14
00:00:40,720 --> 00:00:42,640
a sense of loss?

15
00:00:42,640 --> 00:00:43,400
Didn't

16
00:00:43,400 --> 00:00:44,040
Han Qilu

17
00:00:44,040 --> 00:00:45,360
say anything to you?

18
00:00:47,920 --> 00:00:49,000
So far,

19
00:00:49,000 --> 00:00:51,520
