20
00:00:51,960 --> 00:00:53,040
Oh?

21
00:00:55,120 --> 00:00:56,200
Why don't you

22
00:00:56,840 --> 00:00:58,440
take the initiative?

23
00:01:04,120 --> 00:01:04,680
Qilu,

24
00:01:05,200 --> 00:01:06,320
I've got some great news.

25
00:01:08,440 --> 00:01:10,080
Weren't you nervous
when you got engaged?

26
00:01:10,840 --> 00:01:11,800
How did you know?

27
00:01:13,440 --> 00:01:14,240
Actually,

28
00:01:14,240 --> 00:01:16,200
I was a little nervous at first.

29
00:01:16,200 --> 00:01:17,560
But then I figured that

30
00:01:17,560 --> 00:01:19,480
I finally got the girl

31
00:01:19,480 --> 00:01:21,080
I had loved for years.

32
00:01:22,120 --> 00:01:23,360
Why should I be nervous?

33
00:01:23,360 --> 00:01:24,720
I should be more than happy.

34
00:01:24,720 --> 00:01:25,800
Thanks, buddy.

35
00:01:25,800 --> 00:01:26,640
What for?

36
00:01:27,560 --> 00:01:29,560
I want to tell you solemnly,

37
00:01:29,560 --> 00:01:31,200
