44
00:01:44,480 --> 00:01:45,720
There's no plan.

45
00:01:45,720 --> 00:01:47,720
We are fine now.

46
00:01:47,720 --> 00:01:48,440
My mom

47
00:01:48,440 --> 00:01:50,480
