57
00:02:20,040 --> 00:02:20,640
Is it beautiful?

58
00:02:21,080 --> 00:02:22,200
It's OK.

59
00:02:22,960 --> 00:02:24,320
I'll show you another photo.

60
00:02:24,320 --> 00:02:25,240
Do you think our engagement venue

61
00:02:25,240 --> 00:02:26,240
