65
00:02:32,320 --> 00:02:33,080
Han Qilu,

66
00:02:33,080 --> 00:02:34,360
don't you know ritual is

67
00:02:34,360 --> 00:02:35,480
very important for a couple?

68
00:02:36,200 --> 00:02:36,920
