69
00:02:43,920 --> 00:02:45,240
You're so dumb.

70
00:02:45,240 --> 00:02:47,080
Luckily, I fell in love
with Chenchuan in time.

71
00:02:47,800 --> 00:02:48,240
Chenchuan,

72
00:02:48,240 --> 00:02:49,480
I'll go find Chuxia.

73
00:02:50,520 --> 00:02:51,240
Chuxia.

74
00:02:54,200 --> 00:02:54,800
What did I do?

75
00:03:02,760 --> 00:03:03,640
Hopeless.

76
00:03:04,360 --> 00:03:06,360
Han Qilu is hopeless.

77
00:03:06,920 --> 00:03:08,200
Forget it.

78
00:03:08,200 --> 00:03:08,960
I choose to

79
00:03:10,480 --> 00:03:11,600
