80
00:03:12,200 --> 00:03:13,200
Don't give up.

81
00:03:13,200 --> 00:03:14,480
Pull yourself together.

82
00:03:14,480 --> 00:03:15,640
I will help you.

83
00:03:16,320 --> 00:03:17,320
