84
00:03:17,960 --> 00:03:18,960
Help...

85
00:03:21,480 --> 00:03:22,240
Han Qilu!

86
00:03:28,800 --> 00:03:29,600
Well,

87
00:03:29,600 --> 00:03:32,080
