88
00:03:32,080 --> 00:03:32,480
Ritual...

89
00:03:32,480 --> 00:03:33,200
I know.

90
00:03:33,200 --> 00:03:34,480
I know. I know.

91
00:03:35,040 --> 00:03:36,240
Just let me think about

92
